{"tid":860763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要返工，不了","createTime":"2018-10-13T14:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T03:27:38.000Z","uid":124932,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5639c95926739c6d7ee1a6153a54dc7cb698a1","tid":860763,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"咪再講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多post入面都會見到呢句&rdquo;要返工，不了&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n但其實你講呢句既時候，某程度上你都係想串下香港人咩都返工為主，係打工奴隸，點會唔返工而去做其他唔一定有結果既事<br />\n<br />\n講到好似自己睇透個問題 / 好似自嘲完就冇事咁，其實呢個係一個問題<br />\n<br />\n當你講得愈多，就會潛而默化做好理所當然既事<br />\n<br />\n當每個人都要&rdquo;返工，不了&rdquo;既時候<br />\n<br />\n當下次有更大既苛政，每個人都會覺得其他人都係抱住&rdquo;要返工，不了&rdquo;既諗法，而唔會有人企岀來，所以自己都唔會企岀來，咁就真係冇得救<br />\n<br />\n所以，唔好再以為自嘲完好好笑咁就冇事，雖然下面實有人會話不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e61a65524b6c408a9ebb36aac9ad52ce663dfc","tid":860763,"uid":124932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T22:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a28d89964e4ff4525a2c43eb4335430670a041","tid":860763,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"今日會有幾多人去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd87a79d74e442e38875c59335ceec6c15bf955b","tid":860763,"uid":164167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"打完咁大篇野咪又係安坐家中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇散水之後抽水派全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74a88e0e9837b556bdef66e19399b45cb43807f","tid":860763,"uid":124932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd87a79d74e442e38875c59335ceec6c15bf955b","tid":860763,"uid":164167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"打完咁大篇野咪又係安坐家中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇散水之後抽水派全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔岀去既冇資格站係高地上抽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435d01b919bbdbf3441a256166df4ece39498b26","tid":860763,"uid":116917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"被騙了，仲諗住入黎負皮你"},{"pid":"94b0933e183f4a75b7e21002241a24214dc14938","tid":860763,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"樓主鍵盤勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6589ea09ae22b00f6f565fa7c530a6939a9e0a9","tid":860763,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"講得呢句野得三種人<br />\n熱狗 五毛 自欺欺人既港豬"},{"pid":"9cf4e9f0c1450bacceeffd93bafbd28bdf19db31","tid":860763,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6589ea09ae22b00f6f565fa7c530a6939a9e0a9","tid":860763,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"講得呢句野得三種人<br />\n熱狗 五毛 自欺欺人既港豬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"始作俑者 陳豪賭一場又係邊種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}